Description.value: Update SAP S/4HANA After Activity or ServiceCall in SAP Field Service Management is changed.

name.value: Notify Service Order Update from SAP Field Service Management to SAP S4HANA Cloud

queryOptions.value: $select=ServiceOrder,ServiceOrderItem,Product,Quantity,QuantityUnit,ParentServiceOrderItem&$filter=ServiceOrder eq '${property.ServiceOrder}' and ( ParentServiceOrderItem eq '${property.ParentServiceOrderItem}' or ParentServiceOrderItem eq null )

Value.key: Service Order Header Problem Description Type

wrapContent.value:
<ns1:Messages xmlns:ns1="http://sap.com/xi/XI/SplitAndMerge">
  <ns1:Message1>
    <!-- Target Service Order -->
    ${property.MappedPayload}
  </ns1:Message1>
  <ns1:Message2>
    <!-- Source FSM Event  -->
    ${in.body}
  </ns1:Message2>
</ns1:Messages>

<ns1:Messages xmlns:ns1="http://sap.com/xi/XI/SplitAndMerge">
  <ns1:Message1>
    <!-- Target Service Order Item  -->
    ${property.body}
  </ns1:Message1>
  <ns1:Message2>
    <!-- Source FSM Event  -->    
    ${in.body}
  </ns1:Message2>
</ns1:Messages>
